      <title>自特朗普胜选以来，美国比特币 ETF 流入量接近 100 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/us-bitcoin-btc-etf-inflows-near-10-billion-since-trump-election-win</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自唐纳德·特朗普当选总统以来，已有近 100 亿美元涌入直接投资比特币的美国交易所交易基金，人们押注特朗普对加密货币行业的拥抱将预示着市场繁荣。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/us-bitcoin-btc-etf-inflows-near-10-billion-since-trump-election-win</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 03:56:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国企业债券收益率创下有记录以来最长连续下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/china-s-corporate-bond-yields-drop-for-longest-streak-on-record</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在政府官员准备开会讨论未来一年可能采取的刺激措施之际，一些中国企业债券收益率正处于有史以来最长的下跌趋势中。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/china-s-corporate-bond-yields-drop-for-longest-streak-on-record</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 03:45:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着看跌押注增加，陷入困境的澳元面临进一步下跌的风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/beleaguered-aussie-faces-risk-of-further-losses-as-bearish-bets-rise</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于疲软的增长数据提升了政策放松的预期，且新一届美国政府继续推进关税征收，对冲基金增加了对澳元的空头押注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/beleaguered-aussie-faces-risk-of-further-losses-as-bearish-bets-rise</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 03:38:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>警方称澳大利亚犹太教堂火灾“可能”是恐怖袭击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/australia-synagogue-fire-likely-a-terrorist-attack-police-say</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚执法机构已将南部城市墨尔本一座犹太教堂发生的疑似纵火袭击事件升级为“可能的”恐怖事件，并升级了对该事件的调查，促使以色列总理直接谴责堪培拉政府。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/australia-synagogue-fire-likely-a-terrorist-attack-police-say</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 03:29:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>大型交易不断涌现，印度 IPO 热潮有望延续至 2025 年</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/india-s-ipo-boom-seen-extending-into-2025-as-big-deals-queue-up</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度蓬勃发展的首次公开募股市场有望在 2025 年再次表现强劲，因为投资者对股票销售的兴趣不断增长，鼓励企业筹集资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/india-s-ipo-boom-seen-extending-into-2025-as-big-deals-queue-up</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 03:27:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>药明康德公司股价飙升，因美国生物安全法案通过的可能性较小</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/wuxi-companies-surge-on-slimmer-chances-of-us-biosecure-passage</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一，中国生物技术服务提供商药明康德股份有限公司和药明生物开曼有限公司的股价飙升，此前一项旨在消除这两家公司在全球药物研发中的关键作用的美国立法草案错过了今年最后一次通过成为法律的重要机会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/wuxi-companies-surge-on-slimmer-chances-of-us-biosecure-passage</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 02:29:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国危机和中国数据疲软导致亚洲股市下跌：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-08/asian-markets-cautious-amid-geopolitical-tensions-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚洲股市下跌，因韩国政局动荡加剧，且数据显示中国需求复苏缓慢。叙利亚政府垮台后，油价上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-08/asian-markets-cautious-amid-geopolitical-tensions-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 08 Dec 2024 22:41:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞士信贷之后，澳大利亚将取消 AT1 债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-08/australia-moves-ahead-to-scrap-at1-bonds-after-credit-suisse-hit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚金融监管机构正在努力成为第一个逐步淘汰其银行使用或有可转换证券的国家，去年瑞士信贷 (Credit Suisse) 已不再使用或有可转换证券。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-08/australia-moves-ahead-to-scrap-at1-bonds-after-credit-suisse-hit</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 08 Dec 2024 22:29:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>前汇丰银行家 Nuno Matos 出任澳新银行首席执行官，带来“全新体验”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-08/nuno-matos-to-succeed-shayne-elliott-as-anz-ceo</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳新银行集团控股有限公司 (ANZ Group Holdings Ltd.) 的新任首席执行官明年 7 月上任后将面临一系列挑战。澳新银行是澳大利亚资产规模第二大的银行。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-08/nuno-matos-to-succeed-shayne-elliott-as-anz-ceo</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 08 Dec 2024 20:32:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>政治危机加剧，韩国股市和韩元暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-08/traders-brace-for-more-volatility-on-korea-s-political-stalemate</link>
      <description><![CDATA[受周末政治动荡影响，韩国股市暴跌，韩元跌至 2009 年以来最低水平，导致投资者准备迎接一段时间的剧烈波动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-08/traders-brace-for-more-volatility-on-korea-s-political-stalemate</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 08 Dec 2024 12:53:47 GMT</pubDate>
